208
00:11:55,978 --> 00:11:57,369
Don't, then.

209
00:11:57,369 --> 00:11:59,179
As if anyone's forcing you.

210
00:11:59,179 --> 00:12:00,230
Just refuse.

211
00:12:00,230 --> 00:12:03,586
