213
00:12:08,060 --> 00:12:12,320
Has families fight over a daughter getting educated.

214
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,490
And this is about marriage!

215
00:12:14,490 --> 00:12:16,797
Hold on...

216
00:12:17,597 --> 00:12:20,657
Have you talked about Ashir?

217
00:12:24,340 --> 00:12:25,976
When will you?

218
00:12:25,976 --> 00:12:29,276
When Munir's here with the wedding procession?

219
00:12:33,620 --> 00:12:35,096
Blimey, mate...

220
00:12:35,096 --> 00:12:39,607
Brooding and worrying over it won't help.

221
00:12:39,607 --> 00:12:44,356
I'm sure Uncle and Aunt would never refuse if Ashir's parents came here with a proposal.

222
00:12:44,356 --> 00:12:47,826
And this Munir affair will end for good.

223
00:12:50,606 --> 00:12:52,116
Suboor...

224
00:12:52,527 --> 00:12:55,747
